  line
  line `11. Subs. by Act 25 of 1950, s. 11 and Sch. IV, for "the States ".`
  line
  line `12. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 113(5)(i)(c), for "licences " (w.e.f. 14-5-1992).`
  line
  line `13. Ins. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 68.`
