  line
  line `15. Proviso omitted by Act 49 of 1957, s. 2.`
  line
  line `16. Ins. by Act 23 of 1986, s. 51 (w.e.f. 13-5-1986).`
  line
  line `17. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 85.`
  line
  line `18. Ins. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 94.`
  line
  line `19. Ins. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 78.`
  line
  line `20. Ins. by Act 14 of 1982, s. 48.`
  line
  line `21. Subs. by Act 54 of 1963, s. 5, for "central Board of Revenue " (w.e.f. 1-1-1964).`
  line
  line `22. Subs, by Act 25 of 2014, s. 95, for "Commissioners of Central Excise " (w.e.f. 6-8-2004).`
  line
  line `23. Ins. by Act 36 of 1973, s. 24.`
  line
  line `24. Ins. by Act 79 of 1985, s. 6 (w.e.f. 27-12-1985).`
  line
  line `25. Ins. by Act 40 of 1991, s. 8 (w.e.f. 20-9-1991).`
  line
  line `26. Subs. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 78, for "form ".`
  line
  line `27. Ins. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 113(5)(i)(d) (w.e.f. 4-5-1992).`
  line
  line `28. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 131 (w.r.e.f. 16-3-1995).`
  line
  line `29. Ins. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 78 (w.e.f. 26-5-1999).`
  line
  line `30. Subs. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 108, for certain words (w.e.f. 12-5-2000).`
  line
  line `31. Ins. by Act 19 of 1968, s. 38(i) (w.e.f. 11-5-1968).`
  line
  line `32. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 113(5)(ii), for "licence " (w.e.f. 14-5-1992).`
